column_description: A unique identifier for each student-address relationship
A foreign key referencing the `address_id` in the `Addresses` table, indicating the specific address associated with the student
A foreign key referencing the `address_type_code` in the `Ref_Address_Types` table, indicating the type of address (e.g., Home, College)
A foreign key referencing the `student_id` in the `Students` table, indicating the student associated with the address
The start date when the address became valid for the student
The end date when the address was no longer valid for the student
